metadata.name: RKL Club Anthem
metadata.description:
This NFT is the first of its kind, it doubles as a NFT & a custom made anthem for a Rumble Kong Club.

It can be redeemed for a Anthem that fully represents the Rumble Kong Club of your choice and it's community.

A direct line of communication will be established between the owner of this NFT and the artists involved.
We will work dilligently to make this the BEST anthem for your club! 


This is a madmusic collaboration with TheApeLife.eth

Shoutout to the RKL community for bringing all of us together!
